{"tid":1220833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［齊來打網球］教你選擇合適球拍","createTime":"2019-06-14T05:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T13:14:18.000Z","uid":20414,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f91bc8366e5b22b90e7a70109a094cd3d94249","tid":1220833,"uid":20414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:35:18.000Z","msg":"上星期法網見到拿度第三十九次對費達拿，見佢兩個老而彌堅，又燃起心入面打網球團火<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fuW7Prm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfuW7Prm.jpg&h=e3678abd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，工欲善其事，首先要搵一塊岩自己既球拍啦。<br />\n<br />\n而家啲球拍又輕又堅固，可以輕鬆打到個波又高又遠啦，邊框位又唔會打兩板就散<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Zi-1Ty7rM40\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZi-1Ty7rM40&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=398ed112\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Zi-1Ty7rM40</a><br />\n<br />\n而個透明既球拍套落雨個時可以用黎遮風擋雨又唔會睇唔到野<br />\n<br />\n球拍既 size 最岩身就係遮到塊面既面積加多四份一，咁就岩岩好<br />\n<br />\n大家快啲去買塊球拍，一齊去維園 book 場打衛生波啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oMZEFy9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoMZEFy9.jpg&h=5123332d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6501ad268bcdf9ce4a49c3e377c580ccab2dbe2","tid":1220833,"uid":50363,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:36:28.000Z","msg":"唔得架巴打 太曲無人明架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86472c515aa54d0abc1f7fc382eb62f3a7dabbb","tid":1220833,"uid":20414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:37:36.000Z","msg":"唉屌，本來想開係波台，禁錯 tim<br />\n不過是旦啦"},{"pid":"cb36fee63b95ff339227b8fc8202ce02ab3f3025","tid":1220833,"uid":16839,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:37:37.000Z","msg":"去decathlon買個啲得唔得？"},{"pid":"de5fd72032282558c37eb9134